{"id":144539,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/04/中国开始整治网络水军/","date":"2011-04-14T06:02:29Z","modified":"2011-04-14T06:02:29Z","title":"中国开始整治网络水军","content":"<p>官方媒体新华网报导，中央外宣办、工业和信息化部、公安部、国家工商总局下发了《深入整治非法网络公关行为专项行动工作方案》，从4月中旬起在全国联合开展为期2个月的整治非法网络公关行为专项行动。官方表示，网络水军危害社会，影响正常的网络秩序，将制定管理措施。今年“两会”上，有代表、委员提出，通过完善法律法规治理网络水军。官方同时指责网络水军创造了虚假的“民意”。<img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://solidot.org.feedsportal.com/c/33236/f/556826/s/142f4d7f/mf.gif\" border=\"0\" /></p>\n<div>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/sendemail2.html?title=%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B%E6%95%B4%E6%B2%BB%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E6%B0%B4%E5%86%9B&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Finternet.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F04%2F14%2F0318207%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/emailthis2.gif\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/bookmark.cfm?title=%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B%E6%95%B4%E6%B2%BB%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E6%B0%B4%E5%86%9B&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Finternet.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F04%2F14%2F0318207%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/bookmark.gif\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/100170189662/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/142f4d7f/a2.htm\"><img src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/100170189662/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/142f4d7f/a2.img\" border=\"0\" /></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=L-PptSRXrZs:JiH48CBVkGw:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=L-PptSRXrZs:JiH48CBVkGw:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" border=\"0\" /></a>\n</div>\n</p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.